data.description: Comfort, Convenience, & Profitability! Detached additional unit in backyard with tenant already lined up if you'd like to rent! This charming 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom house in North Fort Myers is everything you could want and more. The beautiful landscaping & fruit trees surrounding the huge backyard make for a serene and peaceful environment. Located just a quick drive away from downtown Fort Myers, you will be within close distance of all the excitement and fun that the city has to offer. What sets this home apart is the whimsical details that make it truly charming & unique. Freshly painted exterior, newer roof and option for solar add to the many perks this property offers. You will love spending time in the cozy living room, boasting large windows that pour in sunlight, cooking in the newly updated kitchen, and relaxing in the natural surroundings in your outdoor oasis. Efficiency in backyard could be rented. This extra income can go a long way in helping pay off mortgage or simply adding to your monthly income. Overall, this 2bed, 1bath home in N Fort Myers is the perfect combination of comfort, convenience, and profitability. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make it yours!
